'''大衛·埃文·麥克馬林'''（{{lang-en|David Evan McMullin}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.legistorm.com/person/David_Evan_McMullin/205052.html|title=David Evan McMullin (Evan) – Congressional Staffer Salary Data|website=legistorm.com|publisher=|accessdate=August 8, 2016|archive-date=2017-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910221143/https://www.legistorm.com/person/David_Evan_McMullin/205052.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；{{bd|1976年|4月2日|}}），是一名美國[[無黨籍|無黨籍]]政治人物，曾擔任{{le|美國眾議院共和黨會議|Republican Conference of the United States House of Representatives}}首席策略總監與前[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]參謀<ref name="swalshe1">{{cite news|last1=Walshe|first1=Shushannah|title=Former CIA Officer Evan McMullin Launches Independent Presidential Bid|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/cia-officer-evan-mcmullin-launches-independent-presidential-bid/story?id=41201256|accessdate=8 August 2016|publisher=ABC News|date=8 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808212632/http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/cia-officer-evan-mcmullin-launches-independent-presidential-bid/story?id=41201256|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

麥克馬林在2016年8月8日宣布以獨立身分參選[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國總統選舉]]，據報導組織{{le|為了美國更好|Better for America}}支持他的參選<ref name="nytimes">{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/09/us/politics/evan-mcmullin-independent-candidate.html|title=Evan McMullin, Anti-Trump Republican, Is Said to Plan Independent Presidential Bid|author=[[Maggie_Haberman|Haberman, Maggie]]|date=August 8, 2016|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|issn=0362-4331|access-date=August 8, 2016|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206185415/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/09/us/politics/evan-mcmullin-independent-candidate.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite web|url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/mckaycoppins/anti-trump-republican-launching-independent-presidential-bid?utm_term=.uanzz99lkj#.fawGG77lWb|title=Anti-Trump Republican Launching Independent Presidential Bid|last=Coppins|first=McKay|date=2016-08-08|website=BuzzFeed News|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-08|archive-date=2016-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010105835/https://www.buzzfeed.com/mckaycoppins/anti-trump-republican-launching-independent-presidential-bid?utm_term=.uanzz99lkj#.fawGG77lWb|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的選戰主打自己是2016年大選中唯一的保守派總統候選人，讓同時不滿[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]的[[希拉莉·克林頓|希拉莉·克林頓]]及[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]的[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]的選民有第三個候選人選擇；而他的{{le|2016年埃文·麥克馬林競選美國總統|Evan McMullin presidential campaign, 2016|參選}}被視為{{le|反特朗普運動|Stop Trump movement}}的其中一部分。

==早年生活==
麥克馬林在[[猶他州|猶他州]][[普若佛|普若佛]]出生，是電腦科學家大衛·麥克馬林（{{lang|en|David McMullin}}）和妻子蘭尼·布拉德（{{lang|en|Lanie Bullard}}）之子<ref>{{cite web|last1=McMullin|first1=Evan|title=About Evan McMullin|url=https://www.evanmcmullin.com/about|website=Evan McMullin for President|accessdate=September 24, 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911143951/https://www.evanmcmullin.com/about/|archivedate=2016年9月11日}}</ref>，其後在[[西雅圖|西雅圖]]郊外成長<ref name=HH>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RNarSHJEOec|title=Presidential Hopeful Evan McMullin – Full Interview on The Hugh Hewitt Show – 8/9/16|first=|last=Hugh Hewitt Show|date=August 9, 2016|publisher=|via=YouTube|accessdate=2016-09-26|archive-date=2020-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200122110428/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RNarSHJEOec|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

他是[[奥本_(华盛顿州)|华盛顿州奥本]]{{le|奧本高中 (華盛頓)|Auburn High School (Washington)|奧本高中}}1994年度的畢業生<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.evanmcmullin.com/about/|title=About Evan McMullin|website=Evan McMullin for president|access-date=September 2, 2016|archive-date=2016-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009132859/https://www.evanmcmullin.com/about|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，高中畢業後到巴西南部當[[傳教士_(耶穌基督後期聖徒教會)|傳教士]]<ref name=HH/>。接著他入讀[[楊百翰大學|楊百翰大學]]，並於2001年獲得國際法和外交[[學士|學士]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865659670/BYU-grad-launches-last-minute-campaign-for-president.html|title=BYU grad launches last-minute campaign for president|date=August 8, 2016|newspaper=[[Deseret_News|Deseret News]]|access-date=August 30, 2016|archive-date=2018-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929191338/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/865659670/BYU-grad-launches-last-minute-campaign-for-president.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；又在2011年獲得[[宾夕法尼亚大学|宾夕法尼亚大学]][[沃顿商学院|沃顿商学院]]頒授[[工商管理碩士|工商管理碩士]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thedp.com/article/2016/08/wharton-graduate-announces-independent-presidential-bid-to-oppose-trump|title=Wharton graduate announces independent presidential bid to oppose Trump|date=August 8, 2016|newspaper=[[The_Daily_Pennsylvanian|The Daily Pennsylvanian]]|access-date=August 30, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115606/https://www.thedp.com/article/2016/08/wharton-graduate-announces-independent-presidential-bid-to-oppose-trump|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

